Note for testing
The simplest way to prepare environment is to source the script like:

==={{{
#!/bin/sh
ANTLR_HOME=/home/netch/opt/antlr
ANTLR_JAR=$ANTLR_HOME/antlr-4.5.3-complete.jar
export CLASSPATH=$ANTLR_JAR:"$CLASSPATH"
alias antlr="java -jar $ANTLR_JAR"
alias antlr4="java -jar $ANTLR_JAR"
alias grun="java org.antlr.v4.gui.TestRig"
===}}}
